{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Sharpen your critical thinking skills in this quiz game that challenges you to spot rhetorical fallacies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2847380/extras/description_title_1.png?t=1736462944\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You know how sometimes people try to persuade you by using misleading or incorrect reasoning? That's what we call fallacies. By mastering <strong>Fallacy Quiz</strong> you might get better at spotting them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2847380/extras/description_title_2.png?t=1736462944\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Being more adept at identifying deceptive arguments helps you recognize when someone is trying to manipulate you. This skill is key to prevent yourself from being misled or swayed in everyday situations!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2847380/extras/description_title_3.png?t=1736462944\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In the game, you'll be presented with various statements and asked to determine if they are valid or invalid. In harder levels, you will need to identify the specific fallacy that is being employed. The faster and more accurately you identify each fallacy, the higher your score!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You can even play the game locally with your friends thanks to a local multiplayer mode, you can play with a friend using only one keyboard, or you can plug controllers to have up to four players! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2847380/extras/description_title_4.png?t=1736462944\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As your skills improve, so too will your ability to discern between logical and illogical arguments in real-life situations! You also have access to an <strong>in-game glossary</strong> of close to fifty fallacies. Be better equipped to avoid being manipulated by flawed reasoning. Put on your thinking cap, and get ready to challenge your mind in <strong>Fallacy Quiz</strong>!</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"5000 Points In Easy Mode","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2847380/19456e1cedeaecc3bd886d27313ab5821bb7270d.jpg"},{"name":"8000 Points In Easy Mode","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2847380/0bcdee4a5aaa7f2a3f10c7ce8eef4c9210d49dda.jpg"},{"name":"Perfect Score In Easy Mode","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2847380/bc81aefd738f02dc44911c262b7fe648cee5bfb2.jpg"},{"name":"5000 Points In Expert Mode","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2847380/9940859109c0b837b88d295d7807c3bba7c073ec.jpg"},{"name":"8000 Points In Expert Mode","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2847380/798ab4aeaef97127c879b1ef3b82bf96180e35ce.jpg"},{"name":"Perfect Score In Expert Mode","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2847380/3a760b6da7d99c2cc6b95cef3b75f655f93e1b48.jpg"},{"name":"10 Correct Answers in a Row!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2847380/b7fbc7226ba79fbb0b403abdeb46c61c9f3ecdad.jpg"},{"name":"25 Correct Answers in a Row!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2847380/fe1b1a75d072cb0970293fece4cb129d1378293a.jpg"},{"name":"50 Correct Answers in a Row!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2847380/43290fb960445893fe4af9fda9bd477084a0006a.jpg"},